summary: This mod ads a windmill shelter located on its own little island, near Ivarstead.If u like a small/compact houses as well as role playing this is mod for you.
descriptionHtml:
Windmill Shelter 2.0
- Few minor objects added, some books subed for STATIC.
- Some lights tweaked.

Future Patch
- Possibility of Nav Mesh for the house - done.

note: For any archers out there, the secret chest is somewhere around the mill.

Windmill Shelter 2.1

Quick update adds NavMesh to the house, I have not tested tho so there might be bugs. if so please let me know.

I would like to thank INSANE OH FLEX very much for making a youtube video:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pR3Ul5ugBZ4

Windmill Shelter 2.2
-Fixes the chest issue
author: Baka
